        <mi>Pa</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>133 "unitsml(Pa)"</asciimath></stem>);</p>
</li>
<li><p id="_d93f2fda-c331-687d-a5f0-dc3385f723d0">the internal diameter of the capillary of the lamp is about <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
