      </mstyle>
      
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>5 "unitsml(mm)"</asciimath></stem>, and the radiation is observed transversely;</p>
</li>
<li><p id="_0bea3439-8e49-5b46-17b1-66c2b34abe86">the lamp is excited by a high-frequency field at a moderate power and is maintained at a temperature less than <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
