<ul id="_dc61d617-859d-c58d-93f2-81346e214b77"><li><p id="_053fb4c7-cad7-a2d7-55bc-3144e482f528">the radiations are generated using a discharge lamp without electrodes, containing <sup>114</sup>Cd of a purity not less than 95 %, and argon at a pressure of about <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
